OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff Airport subsidy
OL,6,FDave Lees, Chief Executive of Bristol
OL,7,FAirport, said the airport welcomes
OL,8,Fpassengers travelling from South Wales
OL,9,Fbut believes competition must be fair.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, he said: "We
OL,12,Fneed to make sure as part of free
OL,13,Fcompetition, we're doing that on a
OL,14,Flevel playing field without this kind
OL,15,Fof unprecedented subsidy, which is
OL,16,Fbeing proposed here today of over #200
OL,17,Fmillion, unprecedented in UK aviation
OL,18,Fhistory."
