OL,6,FIn a statement, Cardiff Airport said:
OL,7,F"The airport is not commenting on this
OL,8,For providing anyone for interview."
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government is expected to
OL,11,Frespond in the second day of the
OL,12,Ftribunal on Tuesday, but in a
OL,13,Fstatement, a spokesperson said 'it
OL,14,Fwould not be appropriate for us to
OL,15,Fcomment' while the case is ongoing.
OL,17,FThe tribunal will finish on Tuesday
OL,18,Fwith a decision expected at a later
OL,19,Fdate.
